# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .env.test — loaded by Vitest (mode=test), overrides the prod-pointing .env so
# tests can never reach production. COMMITTED ON PURPOSE: the guarantee must
# travel with the repo (values here are stubs, no secrets).
#
# Reinforces tests/setup/no-prod-egress.js (the runtime guard). Empty
# GO_SERVER_URL → POST /api/campaigns returns 503 (no outbound). Loopback:1
# Postgres → any un-mocked pool fails fast instead of hitting prod.
# Incident: 2026-06-25 (monkey contract test created 16 junk campaigns in prod).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GO_SERVER_URL=
DATABASE_URL=
OUTREACH_API_KEY=test-key-not-prod
ANTI_TRACE_RELAY_URL=
ANTI_TRACE_URL=
ANTI_TRACE_RELAY_URL_OVERRIDE=
